0. Run the `./scripts/ubuntu-req.sh` script in Chipyard
1. Setup Chipyard
    - Init. submodules
    - Build toolchain (if need be)
    - Source toolchain file
1a. Checkout vitis-integration-ontop-fsim-mill in sims/firesim
2. Run `./scripts/machine-launch-script-ubuntu.sh` in FireSim from $HOME
3. Run Chipyard's FireSim setup script without setting up AWS EC2 items
    - `./scripts/firesim-setup.sh --library --slim-setup`
4. Source the FireSim manager in sims/firesim
5. Run `firesim managerinit` to setup AWS credentials
6. Run `aws-setup.sh` to get the final AWS setup

